<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_5" id="2r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_5_line_1571143158253_602"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jacoben <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Tünfelt <expan>Tümh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü <expan>VVircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> vnd Reicholfen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l2">von Elma / <expan>Pfleg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> deʒ Stiftes cʒü <expan>VVircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_5_r1l5"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / Als vvir <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_5_line_1571143381104_622"><expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von VVircʒburg <expan>verſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſeın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l6">gnade <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / von geleittes <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒunde<ex>n</ex></expan> in die herbſtmeʒʒe vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l8"> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> daraws / Darauf Jr vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_5_r1l7"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> wegen </ab></add> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> vnd vvıder <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l9">daʒ vvir ew cʒwen <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dreÿ tag vor wiſſen laſſen <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / wenn die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l10">in die meſſe cʒıehen vvolten / . Laſſen wir ewr erberkeit wiſſen / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l11">das vor nicht gewonlich geweſen ıſt / vnd künnen ew des nicht cʒe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l12">vviſſen getün / vvan die kawflewte nicht alle auf einen tag <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒwen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l13">vertig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> mügen / . Dann als vvir <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l14"><expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Also <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l15">mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiʒʒe / daʒ Jr an des <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> ſtat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l16"><expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kawflewte / vnd auch Jr habe vnd kaufmanſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l17">vnd die Jren in diſe nehſtkünftige <expan>frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> herſtmeʒʒ vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l18">daraws mit geleitte fürſehen wöllet / . Alſo / vvenn ſie kumen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l19">des begern / daʒ ſie Jr habe vnd kaufmanſchaft vnd die Jren / die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l20">ſtraſʒen durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> lande . herſchaft vnd gepiete </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l21">hin vnd her <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> ſıcher geleittet werden / . vnd <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l22">gütlıch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒe vvıſſen beÿ diſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l23">Auch ſchıcken wir ew beÿ <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>gege<ex>n</ex>w<ex>er</ex>tıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> / abſchrifte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l24"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> briefe / als vns vnſer <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> von Meincʒe vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> von vvertheim</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l25">geantwurt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / den vvir auch in <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> maʒʒ vmb das geleitte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l26">als <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r1l27"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Bartholomej / ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_5" id="2r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jacoben <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Tünfelt,
                                <expan>tümh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü
                            <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, und Reicholfen von Elma,
                                <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dez stiftes czü
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<add><expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan></add>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Wirczburg
                            <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und sein gnade
                                <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von geleittes <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczunde<ex>n</ex></expan> in die herbstmezze und
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> daraws, darauf ir uns
                                    <add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> wegen</add>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> und wider
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, daz wir ew czwen
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> drey tag vor wissen lassen
                                <expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wenn die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in die messe cziehen wolten. Lassen wir
                        ewr erberkeit wissen, daz das vor nicht gewonlich gewesen ist, und künnen ew
                        des nicht cze wissen getün, wan die kawflewte nicht alle auf einen tag
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> czwen vertig
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> mügen. Dann als wir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleizze,
                        daz ir an des <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> stat <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kawflewte und auch ir habe und
                        kaufmanschaft und die iren in dise nehstkünftige
                            <expan>Frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> herstmezz und
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> daraws mit geleitte fürsehen wöllet. Also
                        wenn sie kumen und des begern, daz sie ir habe und kaufmanschaft und die
                        iren die straszen durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> lande, herschaft und gepiete hin und her
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> sicher geleittet werden. Und
                                <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        gütlich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> cze wissen bey disem
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>. Auch schicken wir ew bey
                                <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>gege<ex>n</ex>w<ex>er</ex>tige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> abschrifte <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        briefe, als uns unser <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> von Meincze und
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> von Wertheim geantwurt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, den wir auch in
                            <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> mazz umb das geleitte als
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Bartholomei
                            ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
